                "content": "* Officially documented gameplay changes will be prioritized for these pages. Language and terminology might be changed from the source for clarity or to match the wiki's own terminology.\n* Version IDs and release dates were taken from the PC/Steam release. Consoles might include additional updates focused on improving game performance and stability, or minor bug fixes.\n\n{{#cargo_query:\ntables=SF6_Versions\n|fields=SF6_Versions.version, SF6_Versions.gameversion, SF6_Versions.date, SF6_Versions.summary, SF6_Versions.links\n|order by=SF6_Versions.date DESC\n|format=table\n}}\n\n<!--\nHow to find data page\nhttps://wiki.supercombo.gg/w/Street_Fighter_6/Version/1.00\nhttps://wiki.supercombo.gg/w/Street_Fighter_6/Version/1.01\n-->\n{{Navbox-SF6}}\n[[Category: Street Fighter 6]]"
